        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The anticipation of hitting the golf course heats up as the winter chill gives way to the vibrant blooms of spring. However, with the change in seasons comes unpredictable weather, and there's nothing worse for a golfer than being caught unprepared in a sudden downpour. But fear not, as KJUS, the pioneers of high-performance golf apparel, have unveiled their latest collection, designed to keep you dry, comfortable, and stylish on the course regardless of the forecast.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
