    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Pro 3L 3.0 Jacket: Mastering the Art of Mobility and Protection",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Pro 3L 3.0 Jacket, is a testament to KJUS's relentless pursuit of innovation and excellence. This next-generation rainwear redefines the standards of breathability, stretch, and lightweight performance, offering golfers unparalleled freedom of movement without compromising on protection from the elements.</p><p>Picture yourself on the tee box, ready to unleash a powerful drive down the fairway. With the Pro 3L 3.0 Jacket, you can swing with confidence, thanks to its full stretch body and strategically placed Hyper 3D Stretch panels. These inserts are ingeniously designed to reinforce your natural range of motion during the golf swing, ensuring that not even the rain can dampen your game.</p><p>But it's not just about mobility \u2013 KJUS has thoughtfully integrated cutting-edge technologies to enhance comfort and performance. The KJUS Rain Gutter System ingeniously directs water away during extreme downpours, while the Drawcord Waist System ensures the jacket stays out of the way during crucial shots around the green.</p><p>Moreover, the jacket boasts an array of thoughtful features, including volcanic material lined pockets to keep your hands dry and warm, an ergonomic stand-up collar with a chin guard for added protection, and a new membrane that makes it the most breathable waterproof in the range. From the first hole to the last, the Pro 3L 3.0 Jacket is your ultimate companion against the elements.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
