      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Pro 3L 3.0 Pant: Seamless Integration of Performance and Style",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Complementing the Pro 3L 3.0 Jacket is its counterpart, the Pro 3L 3.0 Pant. Crafted with the same commitment to excellence, these trousers offer golfers a seamless blend of breathability, stretch, and lightweight protection, allowing you to move freely and perform at your best regardless of the weather conditions.</p><p>Imagine striding down the fairway, confidently tackling each shot with precision and finesse. With the Pro 3L 3.0 Pant, you can do just that, thanks to its four-way stretch technology and fully seam-sealed construction. Whether you're bending to read a putt or executing a flawless iron shot, these trousers move with you, ensuring unrestricted movement and maximum comfort throughout your round.</p><p>But the Pro 3L 3.0 Pant is more than just a functional piece of apparel \u2013 it's a stylish statement on the golf course. Featuring a snap closure waistband, back pocket with magnetic button closure, and high-side seam zips for ventilation, these trousers marry performance with style in perfect harmony. With the magnetically hidden shoe flap to prevent rain intrusion through your shoelaces, you can focus on your game without worrying about wet feet.</p>"
          }
        }
